name: Zonechain
description:
One of the first models I made few months back, I had it stored unused, and I think you can take advantage of it.

I really like the way he does the clothes and shoes, maybe it works for fashion design.

It makes nice faces, and for consistency in poses, I highly recommend using open-pose.

It needs extra work with photoshop to correct details.

I will look through my archives for other models I am not using and share them.

In the meantime, I leave my ko-fi if you like to make any request or donations,

https://ko-fi.com/aiposes
